by other friends,

00:51:34.750 --> 00:51:36.335 align:middle line:84%
we have a stronger
immune system.

00:51:36.335 --> 00:51:39.230 align:middle line:84%
Our cardiovascular
system is better.

00:51:39.230 --> 00:51:41.070 align:middle line:90%
Our thinking process is clearer.

00:51:41.070 --> 00:51:42.701 align:middle line:84%
Yes, and you know
joint creativity.

00:51:42.701 --> 00:51:43.950 align:middle line:84%
Yes.
Exactly.

00:51:43.950 --> 00:51:46.720 align:middle line:84%
That is such a profound
component of this.

00:51:46.720 --> 00:51:48.590 align:middle line:84%
Is just be humble
enough to get together

00:51:48.590 --> 00:51:51.010 align:middle line:84%
with your friends or family
members that love you

00:51:51.010 --> 00:51:53.780 align:middle line:84%
and start seeing how-- get
some of their creative input

00:51:53.780 --> 00:51:56.640 align:middle line:84%
